data.description: This home has so much to offer and located in the highly sought after Grayson school district. Rare and hard to find ranch and a half with over 3500 square feet of living space. Beautiful open floor plan, 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths with the primary suite on the main. Finished bonus room and guest suite with oversized bedroom and sitting area and a full bath upstairs. The spectacular kitchen is the heart of the home and open to all gathering spaces. Who needs cabinet space? 42 inch, soft close cabinets. Granite counters, breakfast bar, and center island. Lovingly maintained real wood flooring, 12 inch crown molding, 8 in baseboards, and wainscoting throughout. Coffered ceilings in dining room and family room. Landscaped backyard with covered patio for relaxing and timed irrigation system.
